    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic just split how programmatic Claude usage gets billed. June fifteen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d222898f1ff0cbefd2e3f678395d7b95308043cecd5011a27e700f15d5b2a0bd",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 4.179583333333333,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "If you run headless workflows, this hits you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d832438b1b1123399dc4b005158388beba62dd3f441be34621dd45ffc8ec4653",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.13625,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Programmatic usage is moving to its own credit bucket.",
      "checksum": "sha256:657150db0d490b3664851411293cd6fc63147a60bbd41991ece7f3f73acaa8df",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399583333333335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "The Agent S D K, claude dash P, and Claude Code GitHub Actions stop sharing your subscription quota.",
      "checksum": "sha256:47ec612ecadc0bedd48e27725a1dfcc7819b147f0d09856e165b93e76c4024a5",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 6.037208333333333,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Mark the date. June fifteen. That's when paid Claude plans split into a separate monthly credit pool for headless work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0cfe3bd3b39365f3caf4cad98ae2dfe2037419bed800be8cc51a5c3143f407fb",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.851416666666666,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Not your subscription tier. A separate credit pool.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ae042d9975c99d9d6b33a8fc3f56f17635485deae44b9c8686ae1884af29ec7",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.50775,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Once that bucket drains, your autonomous Kanban, your scheduled agents, your C I pipelines stop.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ba34ad35d2b395af531efe4ea2f30ec09257a4800496b6525a94feeab808aa2",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.690416666666667,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Here's what else moved this week. One \u2014 the programmatic credit split.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f8cd49904ed29e1830ab64fdb8ae573a0b65821ddc665dc2ebf2ea14aa608c6b",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.2507916666666667,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 89
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Ships June fifteen. Two \u2014 Claude Code two point one point one three nine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:53e3c61f17d5c853d66cf1f5e76809d9cf0878cf84399edba3feacb8b90bb0a1",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.179583333333333,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 101
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "The slash goal command runs until the agent thinks it's done.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f1766af75f8dd752b3e98c43223691c192faf325d02b0660593b7d7c99054230",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650416666666667,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 115
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Three \u2014 Cline open sourced its agent runtime.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d3f531a99e014ba5ddc960fe2a2cc6e7291570865b0f2c440bb078b0991fdd65",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 126
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "M I T licensed S D K, decoupled from V S Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e14df3e7719f41c748701d09fd432fde2f050758944d1744ba7c8ae3723ebc4f",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.111458333333333,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 134
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Four \u2014 Anthropic's Mythos scan found one C V E and around twenty bugs in curl.",
      "checksum": "sha256:19e9fc52344d2ddecb3e938403b38151fa0c48e32a7315d89a1d604cd0dd1d54",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.040291666666667,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 146
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Five \u2014 WildClawBench. A real world C L I agent benchmark, not synthetic tasks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:42ba913a59a23f4f5b0e7c6c2a788776c370d5f873da6cf56b7d11daad4ca0fc",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.597541666666666,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 162
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "And six \u2014 Almanac. A self updating wiki that syncs your repo and Claude Code state.",
      "checksum": "sha256:451fd1822f5246ffba184b42a57462f5b0c466f12000ef441c67259f3174606a",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.690416666666667,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 176
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Honestly, here's the thing. Audit your dash P, Agent S D K, and Actions usage this week.",
      "checksum": "sha256:92d42e7136ff6e3f934ca917fce5fd77ff64ba4069c44d7443888e98e2e243eb",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.272458333333334,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 192
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "So the credit cap doesn't catch you mid sprint.",
